===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Smith (2011)}} groups this word along with these items into a word family meaning “root, germ, generative core”:
* {{och-l|荄|id=1|grassroot}}, and its derivative {{och-l|根|root}},
* {{och-l|核|id=2|germ, kernel}},
* {{och-l|骸|(human) bones}},
* {{och-l|亥|sprouting stage}}, i.e. "the moon’s first appearance" > "twelfth earthly branch".

He suggests a derivation from {{och-l|荄|id=1}} by voicing, glossing {{lang|zh|孩}} as “to sprout”; the derivation is not explained any further. However, this sense does not seem to be attested.

